      "content": "Wait, you said the benefits \"heavily outweigh\" the risks. Isn't that a bit subjective? It seems like a lot of people would argue that the risk of a meltdown or the issue of waste being around for thousands of years is way more important than just having cheap carbon-free power. Shouldn't there be more weight given to those concerns?",
